1
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:26,000
When I was young and read the story of marking the boat to find a dropped sword,

2
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,200
I always thought that man was so stupid.

3
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:35,370
Didn't he know that if you drop something in the middle of the river,

4
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:38,500
there's no way you can find it by going to the riverbank?

5
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,520
But after we grow up,

6
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,280
we always return to the riverbank over and over again.

7
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:52,920
We want to use that original mark

8
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:56,440
to find the things we've lost.

9
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,720
Revisiting old places.

10
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,360
Reuniting with old friends.

11
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,920
I hope I can see you again someday.

12
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,680
And tell you,

13
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,960
I am Song Yao,

14
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,210
and this is my best friend, Zhang Yiyi.

15
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:20,940
I didn't expect that we would start here,

16
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,079
and part ways here too.

17
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,680
Old Antique,

18
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,640
I'm sorry we couldn't send you back.

19
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:42,360
Maybe in the near future,

20
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,960
there will be a time machine.

21
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,890
You might just wake up from a nap

22
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,680
and be able to go back to where you want to be.

23
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,079
Even if you don't go back,

24
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,560
don't be sad.

25
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,760
At least in this city,

26
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:04,140
you still have Yaoyao and me as your friends.

27
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,840
This is for you.

28
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,020
After all, I'm your Chinese teacher.

29
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,240
Old Antique.

30
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,140
Take care of yourself.

31
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,880
Do you know?

32
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,560
Actually,

33
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:38,880
at first I thought

34
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:41,280
I had already sacrificed my life.

35
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,760
Everything I've experienced recently

36
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,760
feels like a dream to me.

37
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,480
But,

38
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,640
I might wake up one day.

39
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,640
I hope that when I wake up,

40
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,290
all my good brothers will be by my side.

41
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,960
I will tell them,

42
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,440
we won.

43
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,959
I don't know

44
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,660
what else I will experience in this life.

45
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,880
But I will always remember

46
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,760
the days I spent with you.

47
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:51,560
Is it not a pleasure to learn and practice what you have learned?

48
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:56,640
Is it not a delight to have friends come from afar?

49
00:04:56,640 --> 00:05:01,720
Is he not a gentleman who remains unbothered when others do not understand him?

50
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:06,680
A gentleman does not seek a full belly nor a comfortable home.

51
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:09,920
He is diligent in his actions and careful in his speech.

52
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,320
Hi, Yaoyao.

53
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,240
Yiyi!

54
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,460
Guess where I am right now.

55
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:27,000
Where is that?

56
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,280
I'm at school now.

57
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:31,040
I'm a teacher now.

58
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,200
Ah? When did you become a teacher?

59
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,480
How come I didn't know?

60
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,400
It's not a big deal.

61
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,600
At first, I was quite torn.

62
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,200
I was afraid I wouldn't do a good job.

63
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,240
But unexpectedly,

64
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,500
after I came, I realized it's no big deal.

65
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:46,080
Yiyi, you are so brave.

66
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,480
I really admire you.

67
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,850
What's there to admire?

68
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,880
You persisted in doing what you wanted to do.

69
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,720
What about you?

70
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,240
What are you doing now?

71
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:57,880
I'm writing that paper on the Southbound Overseas Chinese Mechanics.

72
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,680
By the way,

73
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,600
um,

74
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,560
is Old Antique with you?

75
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,220
He went to his driving lesson.

76
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,120
Then tell him.

77
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,960
I'm not just a troublemaker.

78
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,040
Also,

79
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,640
young people today all have their own ideas.

80
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:14,240
Even though many people don't understand why I do this,

81
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,240
but Yaoyao,

82
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,560
I believe

83
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,890
you will understand me.

84
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,360
I didn't choose to lie flat.

85
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,240
My choice is right.

86
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,560
I believe in you, Yiyi.

87
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,240
Keep it up.

88
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,440
Hey,

89
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,440
do you want to see our school?

90
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,760
Take a look.

91
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,360
So beautiful.

92
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,600
I'll wait for you to come back, Yiyi.

93
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,080
Okay.

94
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:38,840
I'll hang up now.

95
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,040
Yeah, bye.

96
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,520
Keep it up.

97
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,720
Bye.

98
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,320
Hear me?

99
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,250
Drive like this.

100
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,400
Drive properly.

101
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,260
Did you hear me?

102
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,720
With the way you drive,

103
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,320
you have to come practice even on your day off tomorrow.

104
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,650
Every day, you never give me peace of mind.

105
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,500
Aren't you hot wearing so much today?

106
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,000
I'm used to it.

107
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,080
Tell me.

108
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,940
How did your license get revoked?

109
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,400
Speeding.

110
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,640
I hate people like you who speed.

111
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,570
You think your skills are amazing.

112
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,360
Let me tell you,

113
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,200
speeding is not allowed here.

114
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,720
You must obey the law,

115
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,800
use your turn signals according to traffic rules.

116
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,200
If you see an old lady walking her dog across the crosswalk,

117
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:35,240
you wait right there until she passes before stepping on the gas.

118
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:35,920
Hear me?

119
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,120
Just drive like this.

120
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,640
However you say.

121
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,920
Let's go for a spin.

122
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,240
Oh! Oh!

123
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,760
The way you drive...

124
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,000
Oh! Oh!

125
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,600
Slow down.

126
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:51,960
Goodbye.

127
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:53,760
Lin Yaozu.

128
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:57,960
Goodbye.

129
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,160
Lin Yaozu.

130
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:03,880
Goodbye.

131
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,090
We will definitely meet again.

132
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,520
Right?

133
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,080
Publisher.
